Class NavigableMapCollectors

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ikueb.collectors.NavigableMapCollectors

  • public final class NavigableMapCollectors
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class providing a set of Collector implementations that collect results into NavigableMap objects.
